PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784249267
OL,3,CScots mother with incurable brain
OL,4,Ccancer treasuring every moment with
OL,5,Cyoung sons
OL,7,FA Scottish mother diagnosed with
OL,8,Fincurable brain cancer has said she is
OL,9,Ftreasuring every moment with her young
OL,10,Fsons because she does not know if she
OL,11,Fwill live long enough to see them
OL,12,Fstart school.
OL,14,FKim Borthwick, 35, from Glasgow, was
OL,15,Fdiagnosed with an aggressive brain
OL,16,Ftumour on January 18, just a week
OL,17,Fafter she began experiencing symptoms.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784249267
OL,3,CScots mother with incurable brain
OL,4,Ccancer treasuring every moment with
OL,5,Cyoung sons
OL,7,FIt came after a busy festive period
OL,8,Fwith her husband Ross and four-year-
OL,9,Fold twins Max and Freddie, and when
OL,10,Fshe developed a headache she initially
OL,11,Fthought she had just overdone it.
OL,13,F"I remember saying, 'I need to lie
OL,14,Fdown'. The headache was unbearable,"
OL,15,Fshe recalled.
OL,17,F"Then my hand started tingling and I
OL,18,Flost feeling down one side. I was
OL,19,Fbeing sick.
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@dO]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784249267
OL,3,CScots mother with incurable brain
OL,4,Ccancer treasuring every moment with
OL,5,Cyoung sons
OL,7,F"I just knew something wasn't right,
OL,8,Fbut I'd never experienced migraines
OL,9,Fbefore so I put it down to that and
OL,10,Fthought it had been triggered by
OL,11,Foverdoing it during the festivities."
OL,13,FFollowing several visits to her GP, Ms
OL,14,FBorthwick, who grew up on Glasgow's
OL,15,Fsouth side, was referred to A&E for an
OL,16,Furgent CT scan.
OL,18,FSoon afterwards she was diagnosed with
OL,19,Fa glioblastoma ` a type of highly
OL,20,Faggressive brain tumour ` and told she
OL,21,Fmight need surgery that evening.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784249267
OL,3,CScots mother with incurable brain
OL,4,Ccancer treasuring every moment with
OL,5,Cyoung sons
OL,7,FShe has credited NHS staff with saving
OL,8,Fher life, saying their swift action
OL,9,Fhas given her more time with her sons.
OL,11,FHowever, she is realistic about her
OL,12,Fprospects, given that if she makes it
OL,13,Fto her 40th birthday she will be among
OL,14,Fthe longest-surviving 10% of people
OL,15,Fdiagnosed with her type of cancer.
OL,17,FShe said the knowledge has led to her
OL,18,Ftreasuring every moment with her sons.
OL,20,F"I don't know if I'll see them start
OL,21,Fschool," she said.
OL,26,@|D@AOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784249267
OL,3,CScots mother with incurable brain
OL,4,Ccancer treasuring every moment with
OL,5,Cyoung sons
OL,7,F"You take those little moments for
OL,8,Fgranted until you realise they could
OL,9,Fbe taken away.
OL,11,F"My diagnosis has given me the clarity
OL,12,Fto enjoy every moment I have with my
OL,13,Fboys."
OL,15,FShe added: "I know I would have made a
OL,16,Fbloody good granny."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUuD@FO]wD@LOUxD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784249267
OL,3,CScots mother with incurable brain
OL,4,Ccancer treasuring every moment with
OL,5,Cyoung sons
OL,7,FMs Borthwick said her experience has
OL,8,Falso brought home the lack of
OL,9,Fattention and resource given to
OL,10,Ftackling brain cancer, where survival
OL,11,Frates in the UK have not changed for
OL,12,Fdecades.
OL,14,FShe said this felt like an "injustice"
OL,15,Fgiven survival rates for many other
OL,16,Fcancers have improved "dramatically"
OL,17,Fover the same period.
OL,26,@vD@\OUvD@fO]xD@WOUxD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784249267
OL,3,CScots mother with incurable brain
OL,4,Ccancer treasuring every moment with
OL,5,Cyoung sons
OL,7,FShe has joined the Brain Cancer
OL,8,FJustice (BCJ) campaign group, which is
OL,9,Furging politicians to provide greater
OL,10,Fsupport and funding for rare cancers.
OL,12,FThe group is also calling for a
OL,13,Fdedicated minister for rare cancers to
OL,14,Fensure continuity in research, funding
OL,15,Fand policy.
OL,17,FShe explained: "I have a fire in my
OL,18,Fbelly to effect change for people
OL,19,Fdiagnosed with brain cancer in
OL,20,FScotland.
OL,26,@yD@POU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784249267
OL,3,CScots mother with incurable brain
OL,4,Ccancer treasuring every moment with
OL,5,Cyoung sons
OL,7,F"It is difficult to accept, but it's
OL,8,Funlikely I will benefit from these
OL,9,Fchanges.
OL,11,F"I can't accept this diagnosis knowing
OL,12,Fwe could be doing so much more in
OL,13,FScotland to support people with brain
OL,14,Fcancer.
OL,16,F"There's been no change to outcomes
OL,17,Ffor people diagnosed with brain cancer
OL,18,Fin 30 years, and brain tumours remain
OL,19,Fthe biggest cancer killer of children
OL,20,Fand adults under 40.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784249267
OL,3,CScots mother with incurable brain
OL,4,Ccancer treasuring every moment with
OL,5,Cyoung sons
OL,7,F"To me, that is scandalous."
OL,9,FShe pointed to the fact patients in
OL,10,Fother G8 countries routinely receive
OL,11,Fsurgery, radiotherapy, chemotherapy as
OL,12,Fstandard treatment, along with
OL,13,Ftreatment using the Optune device,
OL,14,Fwhich slows the growth of cancer cells.
OL,16,FShe said this combination is not
OL,17,Froutinely available in Scotland,
OL,18,Fleaving many families having to
OL,19,Fnavigate treatment options, clinical
OL,20,Ftrials and additional support on their
OL,21,Fown.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784249267
OL,3,CScots mother with incurable brain
OL,4,Ccancer treasuring every moment with
OL,5,Cyoung sons
OL,7,FMs Borthwick also pointed out tumour
OL,8,Fsamples in Scotland are not routinely
OL,9,F"fresh-frozen" during surgery, which
OL,10,Fshe said means patients in Scotland
OL,11,Fbecome ineligible for clinical trials
OL,12,Fand emerging genomic treatments that
OL,13,Frequire preserved tissue samples.
OL,15,F"These aren't cures," she said.
OL,16,F"Nobody is pretending they are. But
OL,17,Fthey give people more time with the
OL,18,Fpeople they love and, ultimately,
OL,19,Fthat's what matters."
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@NO]wD@AOUwD@UO]xD@AOU{D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784249267
OL,3,CScots mother with incurable brain
OL,4,Ccancer treasuring every moment with
OL,5,Cyoung sons
OL,7,FKim is sharing her story during
OL,8,FGlioblastoma Awareness Week, and said
OL,9,Fshe hopes future families might hear a
OL,10,Fdifferent conversation, be offered
OL,11,Fmore options and face a different
OL,12,Foutcome.
OL,14,F"It's too late for me," she said, "but
OL,15,FI want to make a difference for those
OL,16,Fwho come after me."
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@WO]vD@cOUxD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784249267
OL,3,CScots mother with incurable brain
OL,4,Ccancer treasuring every moment with
OL,5,Cyoung sons
OL,7,FHealth Secretary Angela Constance
OL,8,Fsaid: "I am grateful to Kim and all
OL,9,Fcampaigners for their continued
OL,10,Fadvocacy on brain cancer, and welcome
OL,11,Fefforts being made to raise awareness.
OL,13,F"We share their desire to further
OL,14,Fimprove cancer survival and are taking
OL,15,Faction to improve the awareness and
OL,16,Fearlier diagnosis of cancers in
OL,17,FScotland. I would encourage anyone
OL,18,Fwith unusual or persistent symptoms to
OL,19,Fcontact their GP practice.
OL,26,@pD@GOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784249267
OL,3,CScots mother with incurable brain
OL,4,Ccancer treasuring every moment with
OL,5,Cyoung sons
OL,7,F"We published our Cancer Strategy for
OL,8,FScotland in 2023, with a focus on less
OL,9,Fsurvivable cancers, such as brain
OL,10,Ftumours, and improving their outcomes.
OL,12,F"We welcome innovation in cancer care
OL,13,Fand continue to consider emerging
OL,14,Fevidence on new treatments and
OL,15,Ftechnologies to ensure patients can
OL,16,Fbenefit from clinically effective
OL,17,Fadvances."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
